999
01:22:10,857 --> 01:22:13,942
Kita butuh toko baru.

1000
01:22:13,942 --> 01:22:16,945
Sungguh, aku menghindari
setengah dari seluruh lorong.

1001
01:22:16,945 --> 01:22:20,906
Lorong bumbu,
apalagi lorong pastry.

1002
01:22:20,906 --> 01:22:25,909
Dia suka red kites
dan Pop Tart blueberry.

1003
01:22:25,909 --> 01:22:29,161
